      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel so tired. like, every single day is just this massive effort to pretend i'm someone i'm not just so people don't look at me weird. it's never gonna stop, is it? the fighting, the hiding... i don't think i have the energy to keep doing this anymore.",
