      "content": "it just feels less like a \"perspective shift\" and more like just finding new ways to endure the same pain. the struggle is constant. sometimes i just think... if i could just stop, if i could just opt out of the whole thing, maybe i could finally actually be at peace. does that even make sense? that just wanting the struggle to end is a rational thing to feel?",
